  "response": "Here are a few ways to save images from Quora:\n\n1. Desktop Method:\n- Right-click on the image\n- Select \"Save image as...\"\n- Choose your desired location and save\n\n2. Mobile Method:\n- Long press on the image\n- Select \"Save image\" or \"Download\"\n\n3. Screenshot Method:\n- Use your device's screenshot function\n- Crop the image as needed\n\n4. Browser Extensions:\n- Some browser extensions like \"Save Image\" can help download images\n\n5. Third-party Apps:\n- Some mobile apps can help download images from websites\n\nNote: Always respect copyright and usage rights when saving images from Quora.",
